      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:12"
    },
    {
      "content": "下雨不是很正常吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "有必要下雨也提一嘴吗？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "一般下雪天很少会下雨的。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:13"
    },
    {
      "content": "下雨的雪天会特别湿冷，让我想起南方的冬天",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "那么问题来了，下雪天下雨到底是下雪还是下雨？好",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "雨夹雪",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:14"
    },
    {
      "content": "天气正在回暖。",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "嗯，不是应该更冷吗？怎么回暖了？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "啊？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:15"
    },
    {
      "content": "因为回暖了，所以才没有变成冰雪落下来啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "冷天下雨更冷，作为一个资深南方人，你应该懂啊",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "太湿了，感觉我要变成蘑菇了",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "08:16"
    },
    {
      "content": "那每到回南天我就会变成蘑菇",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "08:17"
    },
    {
      "content": "你好啊，小蘑菇",
